<i>and people make their way home,</i>

21
00:01:51,922 --> 00:01:54,114
<i>my own day begins.</i>

22
00:01:54,595 --> 00:01:56,694
Traditional Tonjiru (¥600), Beer (¥600), Sake (¥500), Shochu (¥400)
